• Pattern: double-indirection string table (pointer array → string data)

ENCRYPTION/COMPRESSION ON FIRST SECTION (0x0F8000-0x0FB7FF):
• Entropy: 6.3 bits/byte (compressed/encrypted)
• Single-byte XOR keys 0x20, 0x27, 0x41, 0x55, 0x5A all yield ~45% printable
• Best key 0x5A: 463/1024 printable on first 1KB
• Likely: XOR + LZ77 (same aPLib variant) or custom byte shuffling
• NOT standard aPLib (no 0x01 signature found)

DECODING STATUS: String table (feature labels, weapon names, armor types, UI text)
